Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「期待著你為特集畫的稿子」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…你好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  櫻澤前輩對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒心真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在畫畫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也不是逼你給我看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美奈已經19歲了  要去哪關你什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  美美奈是年紀比你大的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不尊敬長輩以禮相待的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心不要摔倒了哦
